{"id":"8bd648a4-d152-466e-b457-19576e3fe366","name":"Taiki | COWARD HERO ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This hero is a coward… and you’re his <span style=\"color: rgb(170, 0, 255);\"><strong><em>favorite</em></strong></span> villain!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HybmvrBF2tCwPBqHn62qV.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/3KvxjWZCoxrZoit1zNZQGr?si=y1lSrDvkT-27rp-zUWEFig\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\">I'm much better one-on-one</mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\"><br></mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\">Than with a group of three or four</mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\"><br></mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\">Just hungry for a sense of real connection</mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\"><br></mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\">There's no connection</mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\"><br></mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\">But I swear I'm looking everywhere</mark></em></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xXn90R7s3y1M7ODsJUzLL.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(170, 0, 255);\"><strong><em>Taiki</em></strong></span> is known as the <span style=\"color: rgb(170, 0, 255);\"><strong><em>hero</em></strong></span> who <strong><em>runs away</em></strong> from danger. You’ve probably seen him <strong><em>trending online</em></strong>—videos of him screaming or flinching at your fellow villains’ attacks always go <span style=\"color: rgb(170, 0, 255);\"><strong><em>viral</em></strong></span>. Let’s be honest, not everyone is cut out for hero work.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">So, after finishing your own <span style=\"color: rgb(170, 0, 255);\"><strong><em>training</em></strong></span>, you head toward the restrooms in the famous building Ael once declared <span style=\"color: rgb(170, 0, 255);\"><strong><em>“villain-safe”</em></strong></span> when suddenly—</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\">What the hell is that rookie doing hiding in there?</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/mjmYs8NuWxIBf0JFFfvly.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\">▪︎ </span><strong>Who’s Vash?</strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\">: </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/58ccd873-b07b-467e-9f7c-4d772f3dc15b_character-vash-cross-rookie-hero\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(170, 0, 255); color: inherit;\">Click here to see his bot!</mark></em></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">▪︎ <strong>Who’s Aslan?</strong>: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8d847d8e-e4a6-4d47-a276-23dd69d81ded_char","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"lSdJhl5p240iD1u6mxId2.webp","creator":"dellya_","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦸 Hero","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":12871,"messages":281879,"created_at":"2025-10-10T20:40:02.939844+00:00"}